name: Chameleon Zebra Square Print
description: 2009 Arizona's Next Top Model Winner and Elias Nouture Haus Model Gabriel Bustamante, is wearing the "Chameleon Zebra Square Print Tee" & "Splooged Jeans" The shirt is a recycled dark blue 100% organic cotton shirt with a chameleon colored zebra print square patch sewn on. The multicolored zebra print patch is an organic silk fabric which is frayed at the edges giving it a vintage worn out look. The pants are a pair of re-constructured gray workers jean that have been given an acid wash affect to give it a worn out vintage look and a perfect throwback to the 80's as well. The "Splooged Jeans" by Elias Noutureare for sold separately. ALL CLOTHING IS ECO-FRIENDLY AND UNISEX ALLOWING VERSATILITY TO WEAR THEM WITH ANYTHING. THESE ARE ONE OF A KIND, NONE OF THE ARTICLES OF CLOTHING ARE REPRODUCED

name: Catch The Foreign Running Man
description: Elias Nouture Haus Model, Kelsey Davis, is wearing the "Catch The Foreign Running Man Tee" The shirt is a white recycled 100% organic cotton shirt with an image of a running man with a mustache created with multiple recycled fabric patches sewn on. Eco-friendly plastic buttons embellishments sewn by hand are used in place for the eyes. The running man patch is a green and white soy, plaid organic fabric with pieces of jean and corduroy, which are frayed at the edges giving it a vintage worn out look. name: Bobroxemall Weekender Bags
description: Elias Nouture teamed up with, mastermind artist, Bobby Castaneda self proclaimed, "The Greatest Painter Alive" to create these 3 authentic "one of a kind" weekender bags. There are only 3 that were made and once they are gone, they are gone. There are 2 white bags and 1 grey bags that are were altered brilliantly. The weekender bags are a white and grey recycled 100% faux leather with a zipper opening and one zipper pouch on the inside. They are stained with images that the artist was feeling at the moment being spray painted with eco-friendly spray paints and permanent markers to give it a graffiti-esque feel, but still be a faux fashion item without being a faux pa. While one bag may have images of skulls and wordage such as "where we going? LAX, PHX, NYX, MIA", another has the image of half a dinosaur distilled in the fabric. They all stand apart and have unique designs and are covered in art, but still remain fashionably bound. Each bag is signed personally by Bobby Castaneda himself. ALL CLOTHING IS ECO-FRIENDLY AND UNISEX ALLOWING VERSATILITY TO WEAR THEM WITH ANYTHING. THESE ARE ONE OF A KIND, NONE OF THE ARTICLES OF CLOTHING ARE REPRODUCED

name: Suck On My Lollijack
description:
NEW Elias Nouture Haus Model, Chris Hunt, is wearing the "Suck On My Lollijack Tee"
The shirt is a white recycled 100% organic cotton shirt with an image of a lollipop that lays from the top left of the chest leading you to the bottom right.
The lollipop image is made out of black soy denim and organic corduroy, with giraffe animal print in place of the eyes, giving it a unique flair, which are frayed at the edges giving it a vintage worn out look.

name: Rallets
description:
Rallets- pronounced (rah lets) are not only fashionable, but they are made out of recyclable material such as: club flyers, newspaper, magazines, and other paper material.

We take the phrase "Recycle and Reuse" to another level with these lovely wallets made entirely from paper and clear duct tape. We use industrial velcro on the inside of each side of the wallets to hold them together making it more simple for you to access your belongings.

Rallets are so fashion forward and great for people of all ages. Buy one for yourself or as a gift for a friend, either way you will be content with your purchase when you go out and people notice your wallet.

They can be fully personally customized to your taste and liking. They are also great if you want to go with the whole "Green Movement" that seems to be taking the world by storm on a daily basis.

If you would like one custom-made, just send me a quick email at eliasnouture@gmail.com describing what exactly it is you would like it to consist of! No one wallet is made the same, which is what sets the wallet designs apart from one another.
